    why: { title: "The H&O Guarantee", desc: "Why major players entrust us with their promotional procurement and distribution.",
      features: [
        { title: "End-to-End Unburdening", desc: "We eliminate complexity. No concerns about import duties, flaws, or communication. We are your dedicated SPOC.", longTitle: "In Depth: Your dedicated partner in a complex world.", longDesc: "The procurement process of custom merchandise is often a minefield of logistical challenges and administrative red tape. H&O acts as your shield. We take full responsibility for the entire trajectory: from the initial design and quality control in the factory to arranging complex import duties and customs formalities.\n\nYou do not have to worry about defects or miscommunication with suppliers in other time zones. As your Single Point of Contact (SPOC), we offer full transparency and peace of mind, so you can focus on your core activities while we deliver the tangible results." },
        { title: "Transparent Economies of Scale", desc: "We cut out the middleman. Our direct purchasing and volume bundling guarantee sharp procurement rates.", longTitle: "In Depth: Direct purchasing power without hidden costs.", longDesc: "Large volumes require a sharp eye on the cost structure. Because H&O eliminates traditional intermediaries (such as agents and local wholesalers), you buy directly from the source. We strategically bundle our purchasing volumes to enforce the sharpest procurement conditions for our clients.\n\nWe translate this efficiency into a transparent pricing model. No hidden margins on transport or unclear surcharges for customs clearance. You benefit from the scale of a global player with the personal attention of a boutique agency. We prove that premium quality and a healthy bottom line can go hand in hand perfectly." },
        { title: "European Compliance & Quality", desc: "From CE marks on electronics to BSCI-certified clothing, we guarantee 100% safety and peace of mind for your purchasing department.", longTitle: "In Depth: Security for your brand and your end user.", longDesc: "Nothing is as damaging to a brand as an unsafe product or an ethically dubious production chain. The H&O Guarantee means that every product we deliver complies with the strictest European legislation.\n\nWhether it concerns the electrical safety of a charger (CE marking), the absence of harmful substances in textiles (REACH/OEKO-TEX) or the social conditions in the factory (BSCI/Sedex audits): we deliver 100% safety to your purchasing department. We carry out independent tests to guarantee that the delivered quality exactly matches the approved sample. Your brand integrity is in safe hands with us.", showBadges: true },
        { title: "Speed (Near-Shoring)", desc: "Through our Turkish textile hubs, we can act remarkably fast when instant market trend reactions are required.", longTitle: "In Depth: Agility in a changing market.", longDesc: "In the modern marketing world, 'speed' is often the determining factor for success. Long waiting times from Asia are not always an option when you want to respond immediately to a market trend or a last-minute event.\n\nOur strategic focus on Near-Shoring via our Turkish textile hubs allows us to drastically reduce lead times. While sea transport from the Far East takes weeks, we can deliver to the Benelux within a few days via road transport from Turkey. This gives you the flexibility to be more responsive, keep inventory lower, and move faster without compromising on the quality of the finish." }
      ]
    },
